#
# This subtest verifies that the digest fast path in CheckDependencies
# correctly detects canary window expiration. Previously (issue #166688),
# StatsGeneration only incremented on cache mutations (add/remove/refresh),
# so the digest fast path could not detect the purely time-based canary
# window expiration, causing stale stable-stats memos to persist.
